metadata.name: Perimeter Medical Imaging AI Inc
metadata.description: Perimeter Medical Imaging AI, Inc., a clinical stage medical device company, develops, patents, and commercializes advanced in-procedural medical imaging tools. The company offers an optical tissue imaging system, an imaging platform, which provides clinicians with the real time ability to assess tissue microstructures during diagnostic, surgical, and pathology procedures. The company was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
